Package: EpiAwareR
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to the 'EpiAware' Infectious Disease Modelling Framework
Version: 0.2.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Sebastian", "Funk", email = "sebastian.funk@lshtm.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Provides an R interface to the 'Julia'-based 'EpiAware'
    compositional infectious disease modelling framework. Enables users to
    build flexible epidemiological models by composing reusable components for
    latent processes, infection dynamics, and observation models without
    requiring 'Julia' expertise.
